WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.544
Self-Assessment Critique: In light of the incentive-alignment frameworks and causal

00:00:04.544 --> 00:00:09.088
mechanisms discussed, internally formulate a critique of your current approach

00:00:09.088 --> 00:00:13.632
to your top three strategic accounts. Are you actively leveraging

00:00:13.632 --> 00:00:18.176
